                            <comment id="14438832" author="oching" created="Mon, 13 Mar 2006 05:40:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch file for this issue.&lt;br/&gt;
Added parameters for proxy host and proxy port.&lt;br/&gt;
Applied standard maven codestyle to maven-javadoc-plugin.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14438615" author="siveton" created="Mon, 13 Mar 2006 08:32:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think a better approach could be to use user system settings defined by maven-settings. WDYT?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14438764" author="oching" created="Mon, 13 Mar 2006 18:47:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We can set the default values of the parameters to the proxy config in the settings.xml file. In that way, the proxy can be configured either through the pom or through maven-settings.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
